### Date Utilities

Date manipulation and formatting using date-fns.

```typescript
import { formatDate, setDefaultDateLocale, ms } from '@belt/tools';
import { ptBR } from 'date-fns/locale';

// Format dates
formatDate(new Date(), 'yyyy-MM-dd'); // '2026-01-14'
formatDate(new Date(), 'MMM dd, yyyy'); // 'Jan 14, 2026'
formatDate('2026-01-14', 'dd/MM/yyyy'); // '14/01/2026'

// Set global locale
setDefaultDateLocale(ptBR);
formatDate(new Date(), 'MMMM'); // 'janeiro'

// Override locale for single call
import { enUS } from 'date-fns/locale';
formatDate(new Date(), 'MMMM', { locale: enUS }); // 'January'

// Time string conversion
ms('1s');       // 1000
ms('5m');       // 300000
ms('1h');       // 3600000
ms('2d');       // 172800000
ms('1w');       // 604800000
ms('1mo');      // ~2629800000
ms('1y');       // ~31557600000
ms('500ms');    // 500

// Use in configs
const CACHE_TTL = ms('5m');
const DEBOUNCE = ms('300ms');
const POLL_INTERVAL = ms('30s');
```

**Supported time units:** `ms`, `s`, `m`/`min`, `h`, `d`, `w`, `mo`/`mon`/`months`, `y`

